General.Name: CAVA Group, Inc.
General.Description: CAVA Group, Inc. owns and operates a chain of restaurants under the CAVA brand in the United States. It also offers dips, spreads, and dressings through grocery stores. In addition, the company provides online and mobile ordering platforms. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Washington, District Of Columbia.
General.Address: 14 Ridge Square NW, Washington, DC, United States, 20016
